<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>All Days — Architecture Office</title>
  <meta name="description" content="A minimal architecture studio website template with selected projects, studio info, and contact details." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f6f4ef;
      --text: #161616;
      --muted: #6a6a6a;
      --line: #d9d3c8;
      --max: 1180px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .wrap {
      width: min(calc(100% - 32px), var(--max));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: rgba(246, 244, 239, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 18px 0;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .brand {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    main {
      padding: 28px 0 56px;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 46px 0 54px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    h1, h2, h3, p {
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 5.6rem);
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      max-width: 10ch;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .intro {
      max-width: 44rem;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .section {
      padding: 28px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .section-head {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .section-copy {
      max-width: 42rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .projects {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .project {
      display: block;
    }

    .thumb {
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
      background: #e7e1d5;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .project-meta {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      padding-top: 10px;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    .project-meta span:last-child {
      color: var(--muted);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .info-text {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 36rem;
    }

    .list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    footer {
      padding: 18px 0 8px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .section-head,
      .info-grid,
      .projects {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .nav {
        align-items: flex-start;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      h1 {
        max-width: 12ch;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="wrap nav">
      <a href="#top" class="brand">Your Studio</a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="#info">Info</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="top" class="wrap">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>An architecture office working across London and beyond.</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        Replace this line with one calm, direct sentence about your practice. Keep it simple.
        Example: residential, interiors, adaptive reuse, and small public projects.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="projects" class="section">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div class="section-label">Selected Projects</div>
        <p class="section-copy">
          Use 4 to 6 strong images only. Architecture sites usually work better when the project list is tightly edited.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="projects">
        <a class="project" href="#contact">
          <div class="thumb">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511818966892-d7d671e672a2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Project One" />
          </div>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span>Project One</span>
            <span>Residential · 2026</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="project" href="#contact">
          <div class="thumb">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505693416388-ac5ce068fe85?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Project Two" />
          </div>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span>Project Two</span>
            <span>Interiors · 2026</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="project" href="#contact">
          <div class="thumb">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494526585095-c41746248156?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Project Three" />
          </div>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span>Project Three</span>
            <span>Reuse · 2025</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="project" href="#contact">
          <div class="thumb">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512917774080-9991f1c4c750?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Project Four" />
          </div>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span>Project Four</span>
            <span>Competition · 2025</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="info" class="section">
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="section-label">Info</div>
        <div>
          <p class="info-text">
            Your Studio is a practice focused on thoughtful buildings, interiors, and spaces.
            Replace this with 70 to 120 words about your approach, your location, and the type of work you take on.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="list">
          <div>Services</div>
          <div>Residential</div>
          <div>Interiors</div>
          <div>Feasibility Studies</div>
          <div>Planning Support</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="section">
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="section-label">Contact</div>
        <div class="list">
          <div>hello@yourstudio.com</div>
          <div>+44 20 0000 0000</div>
          <div>London, UK</div>
        </div>
        <div class="list">
          <div>Instagram</div>
          <div>LinkedIn</div>
          <div>Send project enquiries by email.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="wrap">© 2026 Your Studio</div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
